            {"en": "They have already eaten lunch.", "de": "Sie haben bereits zu Mittag gegessen.", "fr": "Ils ont deja dejeune.", "it": "Hanno gia pranzato.", "es": "Ya han almorzado.", "tr": "Ogle yemegini coktan yediler."},
            {"en": "He has never seen snow.", "de": "Er hat noch nie Schnee gesehen.", "fr": "Il n'a jamais vu de neige.", "it": "Non ha mai visto la neve.", "es": "Nunca ha visto la nieve.", "tr": "Hic kar gormedi."},
