            {"en": "The restaurant that we visited was expensive.", "de": "Das Restaurant, das wir besucht haben, war teuer.", "fr": "Le restaurant que nous avons visite etait cher.", "it": "Il ristorante che abbiamo visitato era costoso.", "es": "El restaurante que visitamos era caro.", "tr": "Gittigimiz restoran pahaliydi."},
