            {"en": "They wish they had saved more money.", "de": "Sie wunschen sich, sie hatten mehr Geld gespart.", "fr": "Ils auraient aime economiser plus d'argent.", "it": "Vorrebbero aver risparmiato piu soldi.", "es": "Ojala hubieran ahorrado mas dinero.", "tr": "Keske daha cok para biriktirmis olsalardi."},
